Exercice 2
Find the maximum number among given three numbers

Algorithme exo2;
var
nb1,nb2,nb3:entier;
Debut
si ((nb1>nb2) ET (nb1>nb3)) alors
    ecrire(nb1,"is the bigest one");
sinon si ((nb2>nb1) ET (nb2>nb3)) alors
    ecrire(nb2,"is the bigest one");
sinon
    ecrire(nb3,"is the bigest one");
Fin.
